<typeStatus box="[1190,1243,620,644]" pageId="12" pageNumber="11">type</typeStatus>
species name.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="12.[192,707,667,692]" box="[192,707,667,692]" pageId="12" pageNumber="11">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[192,431,667,691]" pageId="12" pageNumber="11">Species included.</emphasis>
Only the 
<typeStatus box="[552,605,668,692]" pageId="12" pageNumber="11">type</typeStatus>
species.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="12.[192,787,716,740]" box="[192,787,716,740]" pageId="12" pageNumber="11">
